item.title: 508 Cache Help
item.dc:creator: @Echo3 Echo_
item.description:
@Echo3 wrote:

So by “seen correctly”, do you mean that you have tested the port for any issues with a port checker? I also don’ t understand what you mean by “done the cache right”. There is no cache editing required in order to be able to connect to a server, unless it is a webclient. Revise your question
